    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>本文旨在手机好用又好看的js插件以备不时之需</p></blockquote><a id="more"></a> <h1 id="Dynamics-js"><a href="#Dynamics-js" class="headerlink" title="Dynamics.js"></a><a href="http://dynamicsjs.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Dynamics.js</a></h1><blockquote><p>Javascript 动画库</p></blockquote><h1 id="Wee"><a href="#Wee" class="headerlink" title="Wee"></a><a href="https://www.weepower.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Wee</a></h1><blockquote><p>minimal front-end framework</p></blockquote><h1 id="balance-text"><a href="#balance-text" class="headerlink" title="balance-text"></a><a href="A jQuery plugin for implementing balancing of wrapping text in a web page">balance-text</a></h1><blockquote><p>A jQuery plugin for implementing balancing of wrapping text in a web page</p></blockquote><h1 id="Trial-js"><a href="#Trial-js" class="headerlink" title="Trial.js"></a><a href="http://markocen.github.io/trialjs/trial-js.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Trial.js</a></h1><blockquote><p>Simple library could monitor mouse position and predict user input</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">可用于预判加载内容，好用。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="in-view-js"><a href="#in-view-js" class="headerlink" title="in-view.js"></a><a href="https://camwiegert.github.io/in-view/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">in-view.js</a></h1><blockquote><p>Get notified when a DOM element enters or exits the viewport.</p></blockquote><h1 id="Fresco"><a href="#Fresco" class="headerlink" title="Fresco"></a><a href="http://www.frescojs.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Fresco</a></h1><blockquote><p>Fresco is a beautiful responsive lightbox. 简洁好用的照片slider.</p></blockquote><h1 id="Slyder"><a href="#Slyder" class="headerlink" title="Slyder"></a><a href="https://cdn.rawgit.com/crewstyle/slyder/f72b904969e18a2ea0454330578d0012239b581d/demo/ind